- Context: This page discusses key characteristics of effective Permit to Work (PTW) systems, emphasizes the importance of people in applying the right controls, and provides contact information for the Operational Assurance Group.
- Text: • Targeted - Used only where necessary

• Clear - Easily understood by all roles

